<!-- Twitter badge -->

<p>Flag your favourite tweets as <em>favourites</em>, send a direct message to one of your friends (both parties must be friends), receive notifications on your IM client or mobile phone.</p>

<p>There is a number of desktop clients available for Mac, and my favourite is <a class="sidelist" href="http://www.iconfactory.com/twitterrific" title="Twitterrific client">Twitterrific</a> (<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/davo39/358544443/" title="Posted on my Flickr account">screenshot</a>). <a class="sidelist" href="http://twitter.pbwiki.com/TwitterPost" title="TwitterPost client"> TwitterPost</a> is another one, but I haven't tried it. Check the <a class="sidelist" href="http://twitter.com/blog" title="Twitter weblog">Twitter blog</a> for more info.</p>
